    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Most developers use one. But Claude Code actually has five distinct customization features.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8448dd11747ace0ef19d55a50db97a0f095286fb25b137b21d8696edef83da3c",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 5.572789115646258,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Each solves a different problem. First, CLAUDE dot M D.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4842591a2f18eb00db59e53ed2b2015724e9d8d2ec6c4656726d298f98ee2e3f",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 3.297233560090703,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 13
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Always-on instructions that load into every session.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6128dedd41639c890e4191ba59438351cac3339f3915bb50f255debe28af4e4d",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 23
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Second, Skills. On-demand expertise that loads only when relevant.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f4e95d431fd5879693ed169d54a1d7eb3978d57185d80c704a998dac56e634b5",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 4.73687074829932,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 30
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Third, Sub-agents. Isolated workers that run in their own context window.",
      "checksum": "sha256:40ebbc1ebbee28e56b23f1eee47830ec9838d3beb64a363c6cacbe9b03c50c7c",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 4.6439909297052155,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 39
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Fourth, Hooks. Event-driven automation that fires on specific triggers.",
      "checksum": "sha256:56066020a2328d8c009ddaae04d446f66efd9f95573a1281f7375fa33a9c5136",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 4.365351473922902,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 50
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "And fifth, MCP Servers. External tool integrations via an open protocol.",
      "checksum": "sha256:09f57df31c6ceb5aabebb8701b45093441132c53b3f6dde373c519083130e867",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 4.783310657596372,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 59
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Five questions tell you which one to pick.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6866af95e30c490b30d5672527ec35ef318751a148231f2fe7c5831408a89795",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 2.2291156462585033,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 70
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Should Claude always know it? CLAUDE dot M D.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a969c5f8900d63279b8612b097b065522d446807613df39253782480da4b2b81",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 78
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Should Claude know it sometimes? Skills.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0008c57796f484daf5ddc3c67eabc6ab4869d68a318d3511046802af08011f7e",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 2.3219954648526078,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 87
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Should it run in isolation? Sub-agents. Should it happen automatically on events?",
      "checksum": "sha256:8e4a81818de329e06b853eff387cc84b92cf13c252c08eb0d5b038ff4c5923b7",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 4.876190476190477,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 93
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Hooks. Does Claude need external tools? MCP Servers.",
      "checksum": "sha256:bf5a46ce1634c60ac955dce0ad9d489cea020efa5ccdc530d736140b93aca520",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 3.9938321995464854,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 105
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Watch the 13 minute breakdown for the full system.",
